                <p class="mt-3 text-[#aaa6c3]">A student-led initiative at the University of Lucknow focused on filmmaking, photography, videography, editing, and storytelling. We bring together creative minds to learn, collaborate, and create amazing content.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-[#1d1836] rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#211e35] transition-all border border-[#915EFF]/10">
                <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer text-white hover:text-[#915EFF] transition-colors">Is it really free to join?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-[#aaa6c3]">Yes! This community is completely free for all University of Lucknow students. No hidden fees, no memberships - just pure creativity and collaboration.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-[#1d1836] rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#211e35] transition-all border border-[#915EFF]/10">
