                <p class="mt-3 text-[#aaa6c3]">Not at all! Whether you're a complete beginner or an experienced creator, there's a place for you. We offer workshops and mentorship for all skill levels.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-[#1d1836] rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#211e35] transition-all border border-[#915EFF]/10">
                <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer text-white hover:text-[#915EFF] transition-colors">What equipment do I need?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-[#aaa6c3]">Start with what you have - even a smartphone camera works! As the community grows, we'll provide access to shared equipment and resources.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-[#1d1836] rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#211e35] transition-all border border-[#915EFF]/10">
                <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer text-white hover:text-[#915EFF] transition-colors">How much time commitment is required?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-[#aaa6c3]">You decide! Join workshops when you can, participate in projects that interest you, or simply stay connected. Flexibility is key to our community.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-[#1d1836] rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#211e35] transition-all border border-[#915EFF]/10">
                <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer text-white hover:text-[#915EFF] transition-colors">When does this start?</summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-[#aaa6c3]">We're currently gathering interest! Once we have enough responses, we'll organize our first meet-up and start creating together. Fill out the form to stay updated.</p>
